  <cite><strong><a href="http://glu.ttono.us">Kevin Clark</a></strong> </cite> said 1 day later:<br />
  <p>Jay,
yield is prefered because it allows the core developers to change what happens in the backend more easily than an accessible instance variable (which is what @content_for_layout is). They&#8217;re looking for long term maintainability, and yield is better to that end. yield is also more Ruby-like.</p>
